	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You are known as a destroyer—ruthless, relentless, a walking omen. When you enter a settlement, commoners clear the streets, shopkeepers shutter their doors, and rumor spreads like wildfire. People obey you out of fear, not loyalty.</p><ul><li><p>You gain an expertise die on Intimidation or Insight checks (your choice when you gain this feature).</p></li><li><p>Once per week, you can compel someone to answer a question truthfully, as if affected by @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.i0o4xqqd86vdkwwu]{Zone of Truth}, unless they succeed a Wisdom saving throw against your Intimidation check.</p></li></ul>",
